HEADWORD: nagami
<hw>nagami</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A shrub (<spn>Fortunella
margarita</spn>) bearing oval-fruited kumquats. See also
<er>kumquat</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> nagami kumquat, oval kumquat, <spn>Fortunella
margarita</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nagana</ent>⟦br⟧
